activities:
LHW will use and otherwise process EU Employee Data in the United States for the following purposes:
  -Workflow management, such as assigning, managing, and administering projects; 
  -Compensation administration, including stock plan administration, compensation analysis, and benchmarking; 
  -Payroll processing; 
  -Performance management; 
  -Benefits and personnel administration, such as bonuses and leaves of absence; and
  -Monitoring and enforcing compliance with company policies and procedures.

LHW will use and otherwise process EU Customer Data in the United States for the following purposes:
  -To process and manage reservations;
  -To better market  LHW’s  services to European Customers;
  -To provide customer service to European Customers;
  -To enroll Leaders Club members and manage Leaders Club memberships;
  -Data hosting;
  -Information technology support;
  -Data analytics.
